            <p><b>Context:</b> User goes out of our app to find exchange rates as currently "Application" does not display them so to keep User focus/attention in the "Application", it was a decision to introduce "New Screen" with exchange rates</p>

<p><b>Requirement:</b></p>

<p>As a bank customer, I want to be able to find out the current exchange rates right in the application so not to waste time looking for similar information on other resources.<br/>
 ++++<br/>
 A user shall be able to familiarize him/herself with the actual exchange rates right in the Application (TBD).<br/>
 FR_5.1: Provide current up-to-date exchange rates.</p>

<p><b>Acceptance criteria:</b></p>
<ol>
	<li>Add "exchange rates" menu item</li>
	<li>Navigate User to "exchange rates" screen when "exchange rates" menu item is pressed
